name: Hermeto
description: Hermeto is more than a memecoin; it's an invocation of ancient Hermetic Wisdom in the modern digital age. Guided by the principles of The Kybalion, Hermeto the character offers investors crypto wisdom, strategic counsel, and a hopeful outlook, transforming the volatility of the market into golden opportunities. Hermeto will keep growing content for his members and users from now on, planning a lot of new features.
